    {
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-6666-4000-a000-000000000006",
      "name": "Market Prices Update",
      "enabled": true,
      "createdAtMs": 1776900000000,
      "updatedAtMs": 1776988973088,
      "schedule": {
        "kind": "cron",
        "expr": "0 7,12,18 * * *",
        "tz": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh"
      },
      "sessionTarget": "isolated",
      "wakeMode": "now",
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "Market Prices Update\n\n1. Fetch crypto prices from CoinGecko:\n   URL: https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin,ethereum,solana,the-open-network&vs_currencies=usd,vnd&include_24hr_change=true\n   Extract price USD, VND, and 24h change for each coin.\n\n2. Use web search to find current prices for:\n   - Gia vang the gioi (XAU/USD per ounce)\n   - Gia vang SJC Viet Nam (mua vao / ban ra, VND/luong)\n   - Gia dau tho WTI (USD/barrel)\n   - Gia dau Brent (USD/barrel)\n   - Gia xang RON 95 Viet Nam (VND/lit)\n   - Ty gia USD/VND\n\n3. Format the message EXACTLY as follows:\n\n   📊 CAP NHAT GIA — {today's date} {current time}\n   ──────────────────────────────\n\n   💰 CRYPTO\n   ₿ BTC: $PRICE (~VND) | 24h: CHANGE%\n   Ξ ETH: $PRICE (~VND) | 24h: CHANGE%\n   ◎ SOL: $PRICE | 24h: CHANGE%\n   💎 TON: $PRICE | 24h: CHANGE%\n\n   🥇 VANG\n   The gioi (XAU): $PRICE/oz\n   SJC VN: MUA / BAN (VND/luong)\n\n   🛢️ DAU THO\n   WTI: $PRICE/barrel\n   Brent: $PRICE/barrel\n\n   ⛽ XANG DAU VN\n   RON 95: PRICE VND/lit\n\n   💵 TY GIA\n   USD/VND: RATE\n\n   ──────────────────────────────\n\n4. If any price is unavailable, show N/A instead.\n5. Send the formatted message as your response.",
        "model": "minimax/MiniMax-M2.7"
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "telegram",
        "to": "1370258715"
      },
